  "Coordinate the real-world workflow behind trusted property listings: inspections, viewings, inquiry handoff, and managed portfolio continuity.": "Coordina el flujo real detrás de los anuncios confiables: inspecciones, visitas, derivación de consultas y continuidad del portafolio gestionado.",
