  "Upload up to four files. Hosted links can still be added in the portfolio field.": "Bulite faịlụ ruru anọ. Enwere ike ịgbakwunye njikọ ndị akwadoro na mpaghara Pọtụfoliyo.",
  "Urgency": "Ngwa ngwa",
