  "Use the download button to print or save this certificate directly from the live verification surface.": "Jiri bọtịnụ nbudata ka ibipụta ma ọ bụ chekwaa asambodo a ozugbo site na elu nkwenye dị ndụ.",
  "Use the exact company account details below": "Jiri nkọwa akaụntụ ụlọ ọrụ kpọmkwem n'okpuru",
  "Use the tracking code card to copy it manually on a supported browser.": "Jiri kaadị nsochi akara ka iji aka detuo ya na ihe nchọgharị akwadoro.",
  "Use your real booking code, for example: TRK-N0RFUKI5": "Jiri ezigbo koodu ntinye akwụkwọ, dịka ọmụmaatụ: TRK-N0RFUKI5",
  "Verification & review": "Nyocha & nyocha",
