  "What were you trying to do, what happened instead, and any error text you saw?": "Kedu ihe ị na-achọ ime, gịnị mere kama, yana ederede njehie ọ bụla ị hụrụ?",
  "When do I get a certificate?": "Kedu mgbe m ga-enweta asambodo?",
  "Where a program is paid, HenryCo may offer revenue share or other instructor compensation. Terms are agreed in writing after approval—they are not promised on this page and vary by program. We never ask for payment to review your application.": "Ebe a na-akwụ mmemme, HenryCo nwere ike ịnye òkè ego ma ọ bụ ụgwọ ndị nkuzi ndị ọzọ. A na-anabata usoro n'ime ederede mgbe akwadoro ya-anaghị ekwe ha nkwa na ibe a ma dịgasị iche site na mmemme. Ọ dịghị mgbe anyị na-arịọ maka ugwo iji nyochaa ngwa gị.",
  "Where the project is right now": "Ebe oru ngo dị ugbu a",
