  "Yes. Assigned programs appear in your account under Learn → Assignments while you complete them in the usual learning room.": "Ee. Mmemme ekenyela na-apụta na akaụntụ gị n'okpuru Mụta → Ọrụ mgbe ị mechaa ha n'ime ụlọ mmụta.",
  "You can paste it into tracking, support, or any payment follow-up.": "Ị nwere ike mado ya na nsochi, nkwado, ma ọ bụ nsonye ịkwụ ụgwọ ọ bụla.",
