  "Documents are path-specific, inspections are real workflows, and managed vs non-managed publication is not blurred together. Calm, but serious.": "Akwụkwọ na-akọwa ụzọ ọ bụla, nyocha bụ ọrụ eziokwu, ọ dịghị ngwakọta mbipụta nke a na-elekọta na nke a na-elekọtaghị. Jụụ, mana siri ike.",
  "Documents read; eligibility and authority assessed.": "Agụrụ akwụkwọ; e nyochara nkwado na ikike.",
  "Each submission is routed by service type, authority reality, inspection sensitivity, and account trust. The form adapts to the path; documents upload directly; the listing stays private until governance clears it.": "A na-ezipu nyefe ọ bụla site n'ụdị ọrụ, eziokwu ikike, mmetụta nyocha na ntụkwasị obi akaụntụ. Fọm na-adabara n'ụzọ; a na-ebugo akwụkwọ ozugbo; ndepụta na-anọkwa nzuzo ruo mgbe ọchịchị wepụrụ ya.",
  "Editorial review path": "Ụzọ nyocha editorial",
