  "Explain the space, occupancy reality, access conditions, and what makes the listing serious.": "Kọwaa ohere ahụ, eziokwu nke ibi ya, ọnọdụ nbata na ihe na-eme ka ndepụta a buru ezigbo.",
  "Filter state stays shareable in the URL, results update without a blunt refresh, and every listing carries trust context before you invest time in it.": "Ọnọdụ ihe nzacha na-anọgide na-ekekọ na URL, nsonaazụ na-emelite na-emeghị mmelite siri ike, na ndepụta ọ bụla na-eburu nkọwa ntụkwasị obi tupu i tinye oge gị na ya.",
  "Find the right place. Keep your filters.": "Chọta ezigbo ebe. Debe ihe nzacha gị.",
