  "HenryCo account sign-in": "Mbanye akaụntụ HenryCo",
  "HenryCo checks": "Nyocha HenryCo",
  "HenryCo expects pricing, media, and listing identity to be strong enough for real decision-making before a property is promoted publicly.": "HenryCo na-atụ anya na ọnụahịa, media, na njirimara ndepụta ga-esi ike maka mkpebi eziokwu tupu akwalite ụlọ n'ihu ọha.",
  "HenryCo is involved beyond publication. That usually means clearer viewing coordination, tighter listing upkeep, and a more reliable post-inquiry path.": "HenryCo na-etinye aka karịa naanị mbipụta. Ọ na-apụta nhazi nlele doro anya karịa, idobe ndepụta siri ike, na ụzọ a pụrụ ịdabere na ya karịa mgbe ajụjụ gachara.",
  "HenryCo keeps this record private first, then decides whether it moves to documents, eligibility, inspection, or editorial review.": "HenryCo na-edobe ndekọ a na nzuzo n'ụzọ mbụ, mgbe ahụ ekpebie ma ọ ga-aga na akwụkwọ, nkwado, nyocha ma ọ bụ nyocha editorial.",
  "HenryCo may confirm access, location, or listing readiness before the appointment is fixed. If you want to move forward after the viewing, extra documents can still be requested depending on the property and next step.": "HenryCo nwere ike ikwenye nbata, ọnọdụ, ma ọ bụ njikere ndepụta tupu emechara nhazi. Ọ bụrụ na ị chọrọ ịga n'ihu mgbe nlele gachara, a pụkwara ịjụ akwụkwọ ndị ọzọ dabere na ụlọ na nzọụkwụ na-esote.",
  "HenryCo uses your account so replies, clarifications, and the next trust checks stay in one place.": "HenryCo na-eji akaụntụ gị ka azịza, nkọwa na nyocha ntụkwasị obi na-esote nọrọ n'otu ebe.",
  "Higher-risk listings can move through extra checks even after they appear live.": "Ndepụta nwere oke ihe ize ndụ nwere ike ịgafe nyocha ndị ọzọ ọbụlagodi mgbe ha pụtara n'ihu ọha.",
  "Higher-risk property submissions stay in eligibility review until your HenryCo identity verification is approved.": "Nyefe ụlọ ndị nwere oke ihe ize ndụ na-anọ na nyocha nkwado ruo mgbe akwadoro nkwado njirimara HenryCo gị.",
  "Highlights": "Ihe ndị dị mkpa",
  "Homes and stays already on managed rails.": "Ụlọ na nnọkọ obibi nke nọ na ụzọ a na-elekọta.",
  "Hotspots": "Ebe na-acha",
  "How HenryCo Property governs listing submissions, documents, inspections, managed operations, and publication safety.": "Otú HenryCo Property si achịkwa nyefe ndepụta, akwụkwọ, nyocha, ọrụ a na-elekọta na nchekwa mbipụta.",
  "If a viewing is requested, HenryCo may still confirm access, location, or readiness before the appointment.": "Ọ bụrụ na arịọrọ nlele, HenryCo nwere ike ịkwado nbata, ọnọdụ ma ọ bụ njikere tupu nhazi.",
  "If assets already exist online, add one URL per line.": "Ọ bụrụ na ngwa dị adị n'ịntanetị, tinye otu URL kwa ahịrị.",
  "If the listing changes materially, it can move back into review.": "Ọ bụrụ na ndepụta gbanwere n'ụzọ dị ire, ọ nwere ike laghachi na nyocha.",
  "If you want to move forward, HenryCo may request identity, affordability, or company documents before the next approval step.": "Ọ bụrụ na ị chọrọ ịga n'ihu, HenryCo nwere ike ịjụ akwụkwọ njirimara, ike ịkwụ ụgwọ ma ọ bụ ụlọ ọrụ tupu nzọụkwụ nkwado na-esote.",
  "Inquiries": "Ajụjụ",
  "Inquiries are tied to your HenryCo account so agents can respond securely and you can track follow-up in one place.": "A na-ekekọta ajụjụ na akaụntụ HenryCo gị ka ndị nnọchi anya wee zaa n'enweghị ihe ize ndụ ma ka ị nwee ike ịsoro ya n'otu ebe.",
  "Inquiry": "Ajụjụ",
