  "Each card opens the full course page: what you’ll learn, how long it takes, whether there’s an assessment, and how to enroll.": "Kaadị ọ bụla na-emepe ibe nkuzi zuru ezu: ihe ị ga-amụta, ogologo oge ọ ga-ewe, ma enwere nyocha na otú ị ga-esi debanye.",
  "Each completed enrollment under your courses contributes to the gross figure. Net payout reflects HenryCo's platform fee per your payout model.": "Ndabanye ọ bụla emechara n'okpuru nkuzi gị na-enye aka na nguzobe. Ịkwụ ụgwọ a chịkọtara na-egosi ụgwọ ikpo okwu HenryCo dabere n'usoro ịkwụ ụgwọ gị.",
  "Each lesson unlocks the next. Finish in order — no skipping.": "Ihe ọmụmụ ọ bụla na-emepe nke na-esote. Mecha n'usoro — enweghị ịgafe.",
  "Earned certificate": "Asambodo enwetara",
  "Eligible courses issue a certificate with a code anyone can verify online — useful for employers, partners, or your own records.": "Nkuzi ndị ruru eru na-enye asambodo nwere koodu nke onye ọ bụla nwere ike ịkwado n'ịntanetị — bara uru maka ndị onye ọrụ, ndị otu, ma ọ bụ ndekọ nke gị.",
  "Eligible learners receive a downloadable certificate and a verification code employers or partners can check online.": "Ndị mmụta ruru eru na-anata asambodo enwere ike ibudata na koodu nkwado nke ndị onye ọrụ ma ọ bụ ndị otu nwere ike ịkwado n'ịntanetị.",
