  "Enter or follow a verification code to see the official record: learner name, course, issue date, and status. This is the same check employers and partners use—no login required.": "Tinye ma ọ bụ soro koodu nkwado iji hụ ndekọ gọọmentị: aha onye mmụta, nkuzi, ụbọchị enyere na ọnọdụ. Nke a bụ otu nyocha ndị onye ọrụ na ndị otu na-eji — enweghị ọmụma njirimara.",
  "Estimated minutes": "Nkeji atụrụ",
