  "Every application receives a written decision: approved, change-request, or decline. No silent rejections.": "Akwụkwọ rịrịọ ọ bụla na-anata mkpebi edere: akwadoro, arịrịọ mgbanwe, ma ọ bụ jụrụ. Enweghị ịjụ jụụ.",
  "Every field here is a server action — saving updates the live catalogue. Keep titles plain, descriptions outcome-focused, and the syllabus tight.": "Ubi ọ bụla ebe a bụ omume sava — ichekwa na-emelite katalọgụ dị ndụ. Mee ka aha dị mfe, nkọwa lekwasị anya na nsonaazụ, na usoro nkuzi dị nso.",
  "Every lesson marked complete": "Ihe ọmụmụ ọ bụla akakwa akara dị ka emechara",
