  "Sign in once. Enrollments, progress, certificates, billing, and teaching applications all live on the same HenryCo profile — no duplicate logins, no parallel inboxes.": "Banye otu mgbe. Ndabanye, ọganihu, asambodo, ịkwụ ụgwọ na akwụkwọ rịrịọ nkuzi niile na-anọ n'otu profaịlụ HenryCo — enweghị mbanye okpukpu abụọ, enweghị igbe ozi yiri ya.",
  "Sign in to enroll": "Banye iji debanye",
  "Sign in with your HenryCo account, then enroll to begin.": "Banye site n'akaụntụ HenryCo gị, mgbe ahụ debanye ka ị malite.",
