  "Some courses are assigned inside HenryCo. Team programs appear in your account alongside anything you chose yourself.": "A na-enye nkuzi ụfọdụ n'ime HenryCo. Mmemme ndị otu na-apụta n'akaụntụ gị tinyere ihe ọ bụla i họọrọ.",
