  "Submitting your teaching application...": "Na-enyefe akwụkwọ rịrịọ nkuzi gị…",
  "Subtitle": "Aha okpuru",
  "Support can review learner requests alongside academy notification state instead of working blind across multiple tools.": "Nkwado nwere ike ileba arịrịọ ndị mmụta n'akụkụ ọnọdụ ọkwa akademị kama ịrụ ọrụ na ngwa ọtụtụ na-ahụghị ụzọ.",
  "Support the academy across courses, learners, assignments, and reporting.": "Kwado akademị n'ofe nkuzi, ndị mmụta, ọrụ enyere na akụkọ.",
  "Teaching opportunities, approval notes, and instructor access should be managed with the same operational discipline as courses and certificates.": "Ohere nkuzi, ndetu nkwado na nbata onye nkuzi kwesịrị njikwa site n'usoro ọrụ otu dị ka nkuzi na asambodo.",
  "The analytics view uses live academy records for completions, certificates, assignments, and review sentiment.": "Nlele nyocha na-eji ndekọ akademị dị ndụ maka mmecha, asambodo, ọrụ enyere na mmetụta nyocha.",
  "The assessment has reached its maximum attempts. Ask the academy team for a review.": "Nyocha eruole oke ọnwụnwa ya. Rịọ ndị otu akademị maka nyocha.",
  "The certificate number is unique inside HenryCo Learn.": "Nọmba asambodo bụ naanị ya n'ime HenryCo Learn.",
  "The certificate remains linked to the underlying enrollment record.": "Asambodo na-anọgide na-ejikọ na ndekọ ndabanye dị n'okpuru.",
  "The course editor writes directly into the live academy store so marketing pages, learner dashboards, and internal assignments stay in sync.": "Editor nkuzi na-edegharị ozugbo n'ụlọ akademị dị ndụ ka ibe ahịa, dashboard ndị mmụta na ọrụ n'ime nọrọ n'usoro.",
  "The course room on HenryCo Learn is where you read lessons, submit quizzes, and download certificates. Your HenryCo account shows the big picture — active courses, saved picks, assignments, billing, and teaching status — in one calm overview.": "Ụlọ nkuzi na HenryCo Learn bụ ebe ị gụrụ ihe ọmụmụ, nyefee ajụjụ ọnụ na budata asambodo. Akaụntụ HenryCo gị na-egosi nlele zuru ezu — nkuzi na-arụsi ọrụ, ihe echekwara, ọrụ enyere, ịkwụ ụgwọ na ọnọdụ nkuzi — n'otu nchịkọta dị jụụ.",
  "The room has recorded the passing assessment in your completion path.": "Ụlọ ahụ edebere nyocha gafere n'ụzọ mmecha gị.",
  "The verification code resolves to the academy record, not a placeholder file.": "Koodu nkwado na-edozi na ndekọ akademị, ọ bụghị faịlụ na-anọchi ya.",
  "There is no automatic “you’re in.” Each stage exists so learners can trust who teaches them—and so you understand what we expect before you invest more time.": "Enweghị \"ị banyere\" akpaghị aka. Ọkwa ọ bụla dị adị ka ndị mmụta nwee ike ịtụkwasị obi n'onye na-akụzi ha — ka ị ghọta ihe anyị na-atụ anya tupu i tinye ezigbo oge.",
  "These path items are ordered intentionally so progress builds confidence instead of creating noise.": "A haziri ihe ụzọ ndị a n'ụzọ doro anya ka ọganihu wee wuo ntụkwasị obi kama ime ụzụ.",
  "These picks are curated to match the topic you're viewing—same clear structure, same account-wide progress.": "A họpụtara nhọrọ ndị a ka ha dabaara isiokwu ị na-ele anya — otu nhazi doro anya, otu ọganihu n'akaụntụ ahụ.",
  "This certificate was issued after the course completion rules and assessment requirements were satisfied.": "E nyere asambodo a mgbe iwu mmecha nkuzi na ihe achọrọ maka nyocha zuru oke.",
  "This course": "Nkuzi a",
  "This course does not include a certificate": "Nkuzi a etinyeghị asambodo",
  "This course may be completion-based only—check the learning room for details.": "Nkuzi a nwere ike ịdabere naanị na mmecha — lelee ụlọ mmụta maka nkọwa.",
  "This is where academy-wide announcements and publishing controls stay visible instead of getting buried inside a broad operations view.": "Ebe a ka ọkwa n'ofe akademị na njikwa mbipụta na-anọgide na-apụta kama ka e lie ya n'ime nlele ọrụ buru ibu.",
  "This page is the live, public verification surface — no login required.": "Ibe a bụ ihu nkwado ọha dị ndụ — enweghị mkpa mbanye.",
  "This reporting surface stays focused on completion, revenue, assignments, and trust signals for finance, internal managers, and academy leaders.": "Ihu akụkọ a na-anọgide na-elekwasị anya na mmecha, ego mbata, ọrụ enyere na ihe ngosi ntụkwasị obi maka ego, ndị nchịkwa n'ime na ndị isi akademị.",
  "This track may not include a credential; you still get a full record of completion in your account where applicable.": "Ụzọ a nwere ike ọ gaghị etinye akaebe; ị ka na-enweta ndekọ mmecha zuru ezu n'akaụntụ gị ebe ọ dị mkpa.",
  "This verification page is ready to be shared as the credibility surface for the credential.": "Ibe nkwado a dị njikere ka a kekọrịta ya dị ka ihu ntụkwasị obi maka akaebe.",
  "Three steps": "Nzọụkwụ atọ",
  "Topics that fit our ecosystem — operations, customer experience, digital skills, partner enablement — get the closest match with our learners' needs.": "Isiokwu ndị dabaara n'ụlọ anyị — ọrụ, ahụmịhe ndị ahịa, nkà dijitalụ, ime ka ndị otu rụọ ọrụ — kacha mma dabaara mkpa ndị mmụta anyị.",
  "Total courses": "Ngụkọta nkuzi",
  "Total revenue recorded": "Ngụkọta ego mbata edegharịghị",
  "Track earnings and request a payout.": "Soro ego mbata ma rịọ ịkwụ ụgwọ.",
  "Track enrolment volume, completion rate, certification yield, and average rating across each course you author.": "Soro ọnụ ọgụgụ ndabanye, ọnụego mmecha, mkpụrụ asambodo na ngụzọ nkezi n'ofe nkuzi ọ bụla ị dere.",
  "Tracked internal assignment records.": "Ndekọ ọrụ n'ime a na-eso.",
  "Try a different keyword, category, or difficulty—or clear filters to see everything we publish right now.": "Nwaa okwu mkpa, udi ma ọ bụ oke ihe ike dị iche — ma ọ bụ hichapụ ihe nzacha iji hụ ihe niile anyị na-ebipụta ugbu a.",
  "Unique academy identities with active or completed enrollments.": "Njirimara akademị pụrụ iche nwere ndabanye dị ndụ ma ọ bụ emechara.",
  "Unlocked after all lessons are complete": "Mepere mgbe ihe ọmụmụ niile mechara",
