  "Video": "Vidiyo",
  "View in HenryCo account": "Lelee n'akaụntụ HenryCo",
  "We approve, ask for targeted changes with written notes, or decline. Silence is not a strategy—we aim to respond clearly.": "Anyị na-akwado, na-arịọ mgbanwe metụtara ya tinyere ndetu edere, ma ọ bụ jụ. Ịdị jụụ abụghị atụmatụ — anyị na-achọ ịza n'ụzọ doro anya.",
  "We couldn't prepare your certificate. Try again.": "Anyị enweghị ike ịkwadebe asambodo gị. Nwaa ọzọ.",
  "We invest in education so customers, partners, and staff share the same standards — and so capable people can prove what they know.": "Anyị na-etinye ego na agụmakwụkwọ ka ndị ahịa, ndị otu na ndị ọrụ kekọrịta otu ụkpụrụ — ka ndị nwere ike igosi ihe ha maara.",
  "We look for real subject expertise, respectful delivery, and outlines learners can actually finish — not hype or recycled slides.": "Anyị na-achọ ezigbo ọkachamara isiokwu, ozizi nke nkwanye ùgwù na nkọwa ndị mmụta nwere ike imecha — ọ bụghị okwu olu ma ọ bụ slaịdị edegharịgharịrị.",
  "We only accept teaching applications from verified account holders. That protects applicants, learners, and HenryCo from impersonation—and keeps your status visible in one dashboard.": "Anyị na-anabata naanị akwụkwọ rịrịọ nkuzi sitere n'ndị nwere akaụntụ akwadoro. Nke a na-echebe ndị na-arịọ, ndị mmụta na HenryCo pụọ na nkwanye onye ọzọ — ma na-edebe ọnọdụ gị n'otu dashboard.",
  "We store your answers, files, and proposal against your HenryCo identity so nothing is lost between systems.": "Anyị na-echekwa azịza, faịlụ na atụmatụ gị megide njirimara HenryCo gị ka ihe ọ bụla ghara ifu n'etiti sistemụ.",
  "We welcome operators, trainers, and subject-matter experts who already help others succeed: marketplace leads, CX and care specialists, logistics and field managers, digital-skills coaches, and similar roles. You should be comfortable committing to a syllabus, deadlines, and learner support standards.": "Anyị na-anabata ndị ọrụ, ndị nkuzi na ndị ọkachamara nke na-enyeworị ndị ọzọ aka ịga nke ọma: ndị isi marketplace, ndị ọkachamara CX na care, ndị nchịkwa logistics na ọhịa, ndị nkuzi nkà dijitalụ, na ọrụ ndị yiri ya. Ị ga-adị mma itinye onwe gị n'usoro nkuzi, oge ngwụcha na ụkpụrụ nkwado ndị mmụta.",
  "We're confirming your payment. Your seat is held—this page will unlock fully as soon as your HenryCo account shows a completed payment.": "Anyị na-akwado ịkwụ ụgwọ gị. A na-edobe oche gị — ibe a ga-emepe kpamkpam ozugbo akaụntụ HenryCo gị gosiri ịkwụ ụgwọ emechara.",
  "Welcome back": "Nnọọ ọzọ",
