  "You’ll hear from us—or see notes on this page—if we need anything else. While a decision is pending, the form stays closed so reviewers always work from one consistent version.": "Ị ga-anụ olu anyị — ma ọ bụ hụ ndetu na ibe a — ma ọ bụrụ na anyị chọrọ ihe ọzọ. Mgbe mkpebi na-echere, fọm na-anọgide na-emechi ka ndị nyocha rụọ ọrụ na otu nsụgharị.",
