  "Available on eligible orders only. Pay the rider when the order arrives — seller acceptance still confirms first.": "Naanị na iwu ndị ruru eru. Kwụọ onye nnyefe ụgwọ mgbe iwu rutere — nnabata onye na-ere ahịa ka na-emecha nke mbụ.",
  "Balance cannot cover this checkout. Fund your wallet or use bank transfer with proof.": "Ego dị adịghị ezu maka ngụcha a. Mejupụta wallet gị ma ọ bụ jiri mbufe ụlọ akụ na akaebe.",
  "Balance payment will debit your wallet and create the order as paid-held for fulfillment and escrow controls.": "Ịkwụ ụgwọ ego dị ga-ewepụ ego na wallet gị ma kee iwu ahụ dị ka 'akwụgoro-ejide' maka nnyefe na njikwa escrow.",
