  "This payment checkpoint stays tied to your Studio project, so payment status, proof visibility, and the next delivery step remain aligned.": "Aaye isanwo isanwo yii wa ni isomọ si iṣẹ akanṣe Studio rẹ, nitorinaa ipo isanwo, hihan ẹri, ati igbesẹ ifijiṣẹ atẹle naa wa ni ibamu.",
  "This payment lane does not show an uploaded proof yet. If you already transferred, continue in the Studio project room or linked support room so the team can confirm the deposit cleanly.": "Ọna isanwo yii ko ṣe afihan ẹri ti o gbejade sibẹsibẹ. Ti o ba ti gbe tẹlẹ, tẹsiwaju ninu yara iṣẹ akanṣe Studio tabi yara atilẹyin ti o sopọ ki ẹgbẹ le jẹrisi ohun idogo naa ni mimọ.",
