  "We could not find": "A kò lè wá",
  "We couldn’t find a shipment for that code and phone combination. Confirm the code on your booking confirmation and use the same phone you listed as sender or recipient. If both look correct, the dispatch desk can verify your record.": "A kò lè rí ìfijiṣẹ́ kan fún àdàpọ̀ kóòdù àti tẹlifóònù náà. Fọwọ́sí kóòdù náà lórí ìjẹ́rìí ìfipamọ́ rẹ kí o sì lo tẹlifóònù tí o fi sí olùránṣẹ́ tàbí olùgbà. Bí àwọn méjèèjì bá dára, tábìlì ìránṣẹ́ lè ṣe àyẹ̀wò àkọsílẹ̀ rẹ.",
  "We never show internal dispatch noise — only the events both sides can act on.": "A kì í fi ariwo ìránṣẹ́ inú hàn — àwọn ìṣẹ̀lẹ̀ tí àwọn ẹgbẹ́ méjèèjì lè gbé ìgbésẹ̀ nìkan.",
  "We render the route as soon as either pickup or dropoff has a precise coordinate. Live rider breadcrumbs join automatically once dispatch shares the position.": "A ń fi ọ̀nà náà hàn ní kété tí ìgbé tàbí ìfijiṣẹ́ bá ní ìkọ́ọ̀dìnétì pípé. Àwọn àmì awakọ̀ alààyè máa darapọ̀ funra rẹ̀ nígbà tí ìránṣẹ́ bá pín ipò.",
  "Weight (kg)": "Ìwúwo (kg)",
  "Weight TBD": "Ìwúwo tó ku láti ṣàlàyé",
  "What you see, and why we built it this way.": "Ohun tí o rí, àti ìdí tí a fi kọ́ ọ ní ọ̀nà yìí.",
  "When a customer files a claim it appears here with their evidence and the shipment context.": "Nígbà tí oníbàárà bá fi ìbéèrè sílẹ̀, ó máa fara hàn níbí pẹ̀lú ẹ̀rí àti àyíká ìfijiṣẹ́.",
  "When a shipment slips its SLA or fails a delivery attempt, it appears here with a recommended next action.": "Nígbà tí ìfijiṣẹ́ kan bá ré SLA rẹ̀ kọjá tàbí tí ìgbìyànjú ìfijiṣẹ́ bá kùnà, ó máa fara hàn níbí pẹ̀lú ìgbésẹ̀ tó kàn tí a gbà niyànjú.",
  "When dispatch assigns a leg or a customer asks a question, the alert lands at the top of this list with an audible toast on mobile.": "Nígbà tí ìránṣẹ́ bá yan apá tàbí oníbàárà bá béèrè ìbéèrè, ìkìlọ̀ máa fara hàn ní orí àkójọ yìí pẹ̀lú toast tó dún lórí mobile.",
  "When dispatch assigns a leg you'll see it here. Keep an ear on the alerts tab — assignments push there first.": "Nígbà tí ìránṣẹ́ bá yàn apá kan fún ọ, o máa rí i níbí. Fi etí sí àpótí ìkìlọ̀ — iṣẹ́ ìránṣẹ́ máa lọ síbẹ̀ ní àkọ́kọ́.",
  "When shipments start landing, SLA health surfaces by corridor.": "Nígbà tí àwọn ìfijiṣẹ́ bá bẹ̀rẹ̀ sí dé, ìlera SLA máa fara hàn nípa ọ̀nà.",
