  "Remove any row before sharing if you picked the wrong file; you can upload again if needed.": "Yọ ìlà eyikéyìí kúrò kí o tó pín ó bí o bá yan fáìlì tí kò tọ́; o lè gbé sókè lẹ́ẹ̀kansí bí ó bá yẹ.",
  "Reserve": "Pamọ́",
