  "Save request and pricing config": "Fi ìṣètò ìbéèrè àti iye pamọ́",
  "Saving commercial config...": "Ń fi ìṣètò iṣòwò pamọ́…",
  "Saving this panel updates the live commercial config used by the public request funnel, pricing preview, and proposal/payment breakdowns.": "Fífi panẹ́ẹ̀lì yìí pamọ́ ń ṣe àtúnṣe ìṣètò iṣòwò alààyè tí funnel ìbéèrè àwùjọ, àyẹ̀wò iye, àti pípín àbá/ìsanwó ń lò.",
  "Saving…": "Ń pamọ́…",
