  "item": "nǹkan",
  "items": "àwọn nǹkan",
  "message in the thread.": "ìránṣẹ́ nínú òwò.",
  "messages in the thread.": "àwọn ìránṣẹ́ nínú òwò.",
  "milestones": "àwọn àmì",
  "pay the deposit, we start in": "san owó ìbẹ̀rẹ̀, a sì máa bẹ̀rẹ̀ láàárín",
  "wks": "ọ̀sẹ̀",

  "A resume is still the fastest way to raise application readiness.": "Atokọ ohun tó ti ṣe ṣì ni ọ̀nà yára jùlọ láti gbé ìmúrasílẹ̀ ìbéèrè ga.",
  "A short, specific note about why this role fits you beats a generic cover letter. Mention proof you have done similar work, when you can start, and anything that affects location or travel.": "Àkọsílẹ̀ kúkurú àti pàtó nípa ìdí tí ipa yìí fi bá ọ mu ju lẹ́tà ìmọ̀ràn gbogbogbòò lọ. Mẹ́nukan ẹ̀rí pé o ti ṣe iṣẹ́ tó jọra, ìgbà tí o lè bẹ̀rẹ̀, àti ohun tó lè ni ipa lórí ibi tàbí ìrìnàjò.",
  "A stronger Jobs profile improves recruiter confidence and gives your application more proof.": "Profáìlì Jobs tó lágbára máa ń mú ìgbẹ́kẹ̀lé olùgbaniṣẹ́ pọ̀ sí àti fún ìbéèrè rẹ ní ẹ̀rí púpọ̀ sí.",
  "About the team": "Nípa ẹgbẹ́",
  "Account-level identity, password, session security and the unified HenryCo trust score sit at the account-hub level — every division (Jobs, Care, Studio, Marketplace, Learn, Property, Logistics) reads from the same record.": "Ìdánimọ̀ ìpele àkàǹtì, ọ̀rọ̀ aṣínà, ààbò àkókò ìlò àti àmì ìgbẹ́kẹ̀lé HenryCo aṣọkan wà ní ìpele ibùdó àkàǹtì — gbogbo pípín (Jobs, Care, Studio, Marketplace, Learn, Property, Logistics) ń kà láti ọ̀dọ̀ àkọsílẹ̀ kan náà.",
  "Active pipeline rows.": "Àwọn ìlà pipeline tó ń ṣiṣẹ́.",
  "Activity log": "Àkọsílẹ̀ ìṣe",
  "Alert saved": "A fi ìkìlọ̀ pamọ́",
  "Alerts you've set up. You'll be notified when new matches are posted.": "Àwọn ìkìlọ̀ tí o ti ṣètò. A máa fún ọ ní ìfòfófó nígbà tí àwọn ìbámu tuntun bá fi síta.",
  "All applications": "Gbogbo àwọn ìbéèrè",
  "All jobs": "Gbogbo iṣẹ́",
  "All roles you've applied to.": "Gbogbo ipa tí o ti béèrè fún.",
  "Any matching HenryCo Jobs role.": "Èyíkéyìí ipa HenryCo Jobs tí ó bámu.",
  "Applicant messages": "Àwọn ìránṣẹ́ olùdíje",
  "Applicants": "Àwọn olùdíje",
  "Applicants on this role": "Àwọn olùdíje fún ipa yìí",
  "Application FAQ": "Àwọn ìbéèrè tó wọ́pọ̀ nípa ìbéèrè",
  "Application submitted": "A fi ìbéèrè ránṣẹ́",
  "Applications already past early review.": "Àwọn ìbéèrè tí ó ti kọjá àyẹ̀wò àkọ́kọ́.",
  "Applications approaching a decision.": "Àwọn ìbéèrè tó ń sún mọ́ ìpinnu.",
  "Applications in active interview stages.": "Àwọn ìbéèrè ní ìpele ìfọ̀rọ̀wánilẹ́nuwò tó ń ṣiṣẹ́.",
  "Applied": "Béèrè",
  "Apply with": "Béèrè pẹ̀lú",
  "As soon as candidates apply, they will appear here and in the employer applicant queue.": "Kéré tí àwọn olùdíje bá béèrè, wọn máa fara hàn níbí àti nínú ìlà olùdíje ti olùgbaniṣẹ́.",
  "As soon as roles start receiving applications, this feed will show the newest candidates entering your hiring pipeline.": "Kéré tí àwọn ipa bá bẹ̀rẹ̀ sí gba ìbéèrè, ìṣàfihàn yìí máa fi àwọn olùdíje tuntun tó ń wọ pipeline rẹ hàn.",
  "At least four clear skills and preferred functions improve role matching.": "Ó kéré tán mẹ́rin ọgbọ́n tó ṣe kedere àti àwọn iṣẹ́ tí o fẹ́ràn máa ń mú àbámu ipa pọ̀ sí.",
  "Audit trail for jobs, verification, and application movement.": "Àkọsílẹ̀ àyẹ̀wò fún iṣẹ́, ìjẹ́rìí, àti ìṣíkiri ìbéèrè.",
  "Awaiting candidates": "Ń dúró fún olùdíje",
  "Back to jobs": "Padà sí iṣẹ́",
  "Basics and identity": "Ìpilẹ̀ àti ìdánimọ̀",
  "Before we call an employer verified, we look at who they are, how they show up publicly, and whether their story matches the roles they post. Pending does not always mean “bad” — it can simply mean “still in review.”": "Kí a tó pe olùgbaniṣẹ́ kan tí a ti fọwọ́sí, a máa wo ẹni tí wọ́n jẹ́, bí wọ́n ṣe ń farahàn ní gbangba, àti bóyá ìtàn wọn bá àwọn ipa tí wọ́n tẹ̀ jáde mu. \"Tó dúró\" kò túmọ̀ sí \"búburú\" nígbà gbogbo — ó lè túmọ̀ sí \"sì ń lọ́nà àyẹ̀wò.\"",
  "Benefits": "Àwọn àǹfààní",
  "Benefits & what they want you to know": "Àwọn àǹfààní àti ohun tí wọ́n fẹ́ kí o mọ̀",
  "Best next move": "Ìgbésẹ̀ ìtẹ̀lé tó dára jùlọ",
  "Browse all roles": "Wo gbogbo ipa",
  "Browse open roles and apply to the ones that interest you. Your applications will appear here with stage updates.": "Wo àwọn ipa tí ó wà ní àyè kí o sì béèrè fún èyí tí ó wù ọ́. Àwọn ìbéèrè rẹ máa fara hàn níbí pẹ̀lú ìmúdátọ́jú ìpele.",
  "Build a shortlist worth revisiting.": "Kọ́ àkójọ kúkurú tó tọ́ láti tún wo.",
  "Built from profile completeness, verification status, and hiring activity.": "A kọ́ láti inú ìpé profáìlì, ipò ìjẹ́rìí, àti ìṣe ìgbaniṣẹ́.",
  "Candidate": "Olùdíje",
  "Candidate Detail": "Àlàyé olùdíje",
  "Candidate hub": "Ibùdó olùdíje",
  "Candidate movement will appear here.": "Ìṣíkiri olùdíje máa fara hàn níbí.",
  "Candidate profiles": "Àwọn profáìlì olùdíje",
  "Candidates": "Àwọn olùdíje",
  "Candidates across your roles.": "Àwọn olùdíje láàrín àwọn ipa rẹ.",
  "Candidates and employers use the same platform with different workspaces. If something here does not match what you see on screen, contact": "Àwọn olùdíje àti àwọn olùgbaniṣẹ́ ń lo pẹpẹ kan náà pẹ̀lú àwọn ojú-ìwé iṣẹ́ tó yàtọ̀. Bí nǹkan kan níbí kò bá bá ohun tí o rí lójú-ìwé mu, kàn sí",
  "Careers at HenryCo": "Iṣẹ́ ní HenryCo",
  "Category slug": "Slug ẹ̀ka",
  "Check back later or browse other open positions on the board.": "Padà lẹ́yìn náà tàbí ṣàwárí àwọn ipa mìíràn tó wà ní àyè lórí pátákó.",
  "Check back soon or browse external roles from verified employers on the main board.": "Padà laipẹ tàbí ṣàwárí àwọn ipa òde láti ọ̀dọ̀ olùgbaniṣẹ́ tí a ti fọwọ́sí lórí pátákó pàtàkì.",
  "Check pay, title, start date, and who you report to. It is OK to ask quiet questions before you say yes.": "Yẹ owó, orúkọ ipa, ọjọ́ ìbẹ̀rẹ̀, àti ẹni tí o máa ròyìn fún. Kò sí ìṣòro láti bi àwọn ìbéèrè jẹ́jẹ́ kí o tó sọ bẹ́ẹ̀ ni.",
  "Communication": "Ìbánisọ̀rọ̀",
