  "Contact collision review": "Àyẹ̀wò ìkọlu ìbáṣe",
  "Coordinate the real-world workflow behind trusted property listings: inspections, viewings, inquiry handoff, and managed portfolio continuity.": "Ṣàkóso ìṣàn iṣẹ́ ayé gangan tó wà lẹ́yìn àwọn àkọsílẹ̀ ohun-ìní tó dára: àyẹ̀wò, ìwòye, ìtìpa-ẹnu ìbéèrè, àti ìtẹ̀síwájú portfolio tí a ń ṣàkóso.",
