  "Docs hold": "Àwọn ìwé tí a dúró",
  "Documents": "Àwọn ìwé",
  "Documents are path-specific, inspections are real workflows, and managed vs non-managed publication is not blurred together. Calm, but serious.": "Àwọn ìwé jẹ́ ti ọ̀nà kọ̀ọ̀kan, àyẹ̀wò jẹ́ àwọn ìṣàn iṣẹ́ gidi, kò sì sí ìdàrú láàárín ìtẹ̀jáde tí a ń ṣàkóso àti aláìní ìṣàkóso. Dákẹ́, ṣùgbọ́n pàtàkì.",
  "Documents read; eligibility and authority assessed.": "A ka àwọn ìwé; a sì ṣe ìdájọ́ yíyẹ àti aláṣẹ.",
  "Each submission is routed by service type, authority reality, inspection sensitivity, and account trust. The form adapts to the path; documents upload directly; the listing stays private until governance clears it.": "Ìfilọ́lẹ̀ kọ̀ọ̀kan ni a ń darí nípa irú iṣẹ́, òtítọ́ aláṣẹ, ìmọ̀lára àyẹ̀wò, àti ìgbẹ́kẹ̀lé àkàǹtì. Fọ́ọ̀mù máa ń bá ọ̀nà mu; àwọn ìwé tí a gbé sókè tààrà; àkọsílẹ̀ máa wà ní àdàádúkíá títí ti ìṣàkóso fi fọwọ́sí.",
  "Editorial review path": "Ọ̀nà àyẹ̀wò ìròyìn",
  "Editorial review, approval, then publication if quality holds.": "Àyẹ̀wò ìròyìn, ìfọwọ́sí, lẹ́yìn náà ìtẹ̀jáde tí ìwà bá dúró.",
  "Eligibility": "Yíyẹ",
  "Eligibility hold": "Ìdúró yíyẹ",
  "Email and WhatsApp delivery stack for property notifications.": "Òkìtì ìfìránṣẹ́ imeeli àti WhatsApp fún ìfòfófó ohun-ìní.",
  "Escalated": "A gbé sókè",
  "Existing media URLs": "Àwọn URL media tó wà",
  "Expected response": "Ìdáhùn tí a retí",
  "Explain the space, occupancy reality, access conditions, and what makes the listing serious.": "Ṣàlàyé àyè náà, òtítọ́ ìbárayé, ipò ìwọlé, àti ohun tó mú àkọsílẹ̀ jẹ́ pàtàkì.",
  "Filter state stays shareable in the URL, results update without a blunt refresh, and every listing carries trust context before you invest time in it.": "Ipò àsẹ́ ń wà ní pípín nínú URL, àbájáde ń ṣe àtúnṣe láìní àtúntán líle, gbogbo àkọsílẹ̀ sì ń gbé àyíká ìgbẹ́kẹ̀lé kí o tó fi àkókò rẹ sí.",
  "Find the right place. Keep your filters.": "Wá ibi tó tọ́. Pa àwọn àsẹ́ rẹ mọ́.",
