  "The team is on the way to the property.": "Tawagar tana kan hanyar zuwa dukiya.",
  "The team reviews the request after submission. The amount shown here reflects the current estimate based on the details you selected above.": "Tawagar tana duba buƙatar bayan ƙaddamarwa. Adadin da aka nuna anan yana nuna ƙimar halin yanzu dangane da cikakkun bayanai da kuka zaɓa a sama.",
  "The visit is complete and the customer follow-up stage is open.": "Ziyarar ta cika kuma matakin bin abokin ciniki yana buɗe.",
  "The workspace cleaning scope is actively in progress.": "Wurin tsaftace sararin aiki yana kan ci gaba sosai.",
  "This does not skip booking review. It simply opens the payment path immediately so the team can confirm your payment faster.": "Wannan baya tsallake bitar yin rajista. Kawai yana buɗe hanyar biyan kuɗi nan da nan don ƙungiyar ta iya tabbatar da biyan ku cikin sauri.",
  "This payment checkpoint stays tied to your Studio project, so payment status, proof visibility, and the next delivery step remain aligned.": "Wannan wurin bincike na biyan kuɗi yana daura da aikin Studio ɗin ku, don haka matsayin biyan kuɗi, ganuwa hujja, da matakin isarwa na gaba sun kasance masu daidaitawa.",
  "This payment lane does not show an uploaded proof yet. If you already transferred, continue in the Studio project room or linked support room so the team can confirm the deposit cleanly.": "Wannan layin biyan kuɗi bai nuna shaidar da aka ɗora ba tukuna. Idan kun riga kun canza wurin, ci gaba a cikin ɗakin aikin Studio ko ɗakin tallafi da aka haɗa don ƙungiyar ta iya tabbatar da ajiyar kuɗi cikin tsafta.",
  "This service has been completed, so you can now share a verified review linked to your tracking code and booking phone number.": "An kammala wannan sabis ɗin, don haka yanzu za ku iya raba tabbataccen bita da ke da alaƙa da lambar bin diddigin ku da lambar wayar ajiyar kuɗi.",
  "Timing preference": "Zaɓin lokaci",
