  "Topics that fit our ecosystem—operations, customer experience, digital skills, and partner enablement—get the closest match with our learners’ needs.": "Batutuwan da suka dace da yanayin yanayin mu—ayyukan aiki, ƙwarewar abokin ciniki, ƙwarewar dijital, da baiwa abokin tarayya—suna samun mafi kusancin dacewa da bukatun ɗaliban mu.",
