  "Use the download button to print or save this certificate directly from the live verification surface.": "Yi amfani da maɓallin zazzagewa don bugawa ko adana wannan takaddun shaida kai tsaye daga saman tabbatarwa kai tsaye.",
  "Use the exact company account details below": "Yi amfani da ainihin bayanan asusun kamfanin da ke ƙasa",
  "Use the tracking code card to copy it manually on a supported browser.": "Yi amfani da katin sa ido don kwafe shi da hannu akan mai bincike mai goyan baya.",
