  "This route is read-only. It only reflects subscription rows that a division has already written into `customer_subscriptions`.": "Wannan hanya karantawa kawai ce. Tana nuna layukan biyan kuɗi ne kawai da wani sashe ya riga ya rubuta a cikin `customer_subscriptions`.",
  "Management is still owned by the division workspace. The account hub can deep-link you there, but it does not mutate subscription state directly.": "Har yanzu wurin aikin sashen ne ke kula da shi. Cibiyar asusu za ta iya kai ka can kai tsaye, amma ba ta canza halin biyan kuɗin kai tsaye ba.",
  "No direct management route has been published for this division inside the account hub yet, so there is no manage action to expose here.": "Har yanzu ba a wallafa hanyar gudanarwa kai tsaye ga wannan sashe a cikin cibiyar asusu ba, saboda haka babu aikin gudanarwa da za a nuna a nan.",
  "Linked invoices and support threads below are shown only when the shared ledger uses one of this subscription's published reference keys.": "Ana nuna invoice da zaren tallafi na ƙasa ne kawai idan littafin haɗin gwiwa yana amfani da ɗaya daga cikin maɓallan tunani da aka wallafa na wannan biyan kuɗi.",
  "This subscription row has no published reference key beyond its own record, so invoice/support linkage depends entirely on future division-side sync quality.": "Wannan layin biyan kuɗi ba shi da wani maɓallin tunani da aka wallafa bayan nasa rikodin, saboda haka haɗin invoice da tallafi ya dogara gaba ɗaya da ingancin daidaitawar sashen a nan gaba.",
