  "Volume customers with negotiated SLA + billing terms. Bulk shipment composer lives inside the customer-side B2B admin.": "Abokan ciniki masu yawa tare da SLA da sharuɗɗan biya da aka tattauna. Mai tsara aikawa mai yawa yana cikin admin na B2B na bangaren abokin ciniki.",
  "Volume, on-time %, exceptions, revenue, and fleet utilisation. Click a metric for the per-corridor breakdown.": "Yawa, kashi na kan lokaci, banbance-banbance, kuɗin shiga, da amfani da tasoshin. Latsa awo don raba bisa kowace hanya.",
  "We could not find": "Ba mu iya samun ba",
  "We couldn’t find a shipment for that code and phone combination. Confirm the code on your booking confirmation and use the same phone you listed as sender or recipient. If both look correct, the dispatch desk can verify your record.": "Ba mu iya samun aikawa don wannan haɗin lambar da wayar ba. Tabbatar da lambar a tabbatar da rajistarka kuma ka yi amfani da waya guda da ka jera a matsayin mai aikawa ko mai karɓa. Idan duka biyu suna kama da daidai, teburin tura zai iya tabbatar da rikodin ka.",
  "We never show internal dispatch noise — only the events both sides can act on.": "Ba mu taɓa nuna hayaniya ta cikin tura — kawai abubuwan da ɓangarorin biyu za su iya yi.",
  "We render the route as soon as either pickup or dropoff has a precise coordinate. Live rider breadcrumbs join automatically once dispatch shares the position.": "Muna nuna hanya da zarar an samu daidaitaccen wuri na ɗauka ko sauka. Alamomin mai aiki kai tsaye suna haɗawa ta atomatik da zarar tura ya raba wurin.",
  "Weight (kg)": "Nauyi (kg)",
  "Weight TBD": "Nauyi mai jiran tabbatarwa",
  "What you see, and why we built it this way.": "Abin da kake gani, da kuma dalilin da yasa muka gina shi haka.",
  "When a customer files a claim it appears here with their evidence and the shipment context.": "Lokacin da abokin ciniki ya gabatar da korafi, yana bayyana a nan tare da hujjarsa da yanayin aikawa.",
  "When a shipment slips its SLA or fails a delivery attempt, it appears here with a recommended next action.": "Lokacin da aikawa ya wuce SLA dinsa ko ya gaza ƙoƙarin bayarwa, yana bayyana a nan tare da matakin gaba da aka ba da shawara.",
  "When dispatch assigns a leg or a customer asks a question, the alert lands at the top of this list with an audible toast on mobile.": "Lokacin da tura ya sanya sashe ko abokin ciniki ya yi tambaya, faɗakarwa tana fitowa a saman wannan jeri tare da toast mai sauti a wayar hannu.",
  "When dispatch assigns a leg you'll see it here. Keep an ear on the alerts tab — assignments push there first.": "Lokacin da tura ya sanya maka sashe za ka gan shi a nan. Yi kunne ga shafin faɗakarwa — sanya ayyuka suna fara zuwa can.",
  "When shipments start landing, SLA health surfaces by corridor.": "Lokacin da aikawa za su fara zuwa, lafiyar SLA za ta bayyana ta kowace hanya.",
  "When you have a shipment, this page shows the customer contact, pickup + dropoff detail, and the POD capture form.": "Lokacin da kake da aikawa, wannan shafin yana nuna lambar abokin ciniki, bayanin ɗauka + sauka, da fom ɗin ɗaukar POD.",
  "Where our rider or dispatch team should collect the parcel.": "Inda mai aikinmu ko ƙungiyar tura za su ɗauki fakitin.",
