  "If you serve one country strongly, your local registrar may offer a trusted country ending—we will confirm what fits your brand.": "Idan kana yi wa wata ƙasa hidima sosai, mai rajistar yankinka na iya bayar da ƙarewar ƙasa abin amincewa — za mu tabbatar abin da ya dace da alamarka.",
