  "Real prices. Real timelines. We tailor the chosen site to your brand and content, then launch.": "Farashi na gaskiya. Lokuta na gaskiya. Muna daidaita shafin da aka zaɓa zuwa alamarka da abubuwan ciki, sannan mu fitar.",
