  "Remove": "Cire",
  "Remove any row before sharing if you picked the wrong file; you can upload again if needed.": "Cire kowane layi kafin raba idan ka zaɓi fayil ɗin da bai dace ba; za ka iya ɗora kuma idan an buƙata.",
  "Reserve": "Riƙe",
