  "A resume is still the fastest way to raise application readiness.": "Takardar bayani har yanzu ita ce hanya mafi sauri don ƙara shirye-shiryen aikace-aikace.",
  "A short, specific note about why this role fits you beats a generic cover letter. Mention proof you have done similar work, when you can start, and anything that affects location or travel.": "Gajeren bayani da takamaiman dalili akan dalilin da yasa wannan matsayin ya dace da ku ya fi wasiƙar rufawa ta gaba ɗaya. Ambata hujjar yin irin wannan aiki, lokacin da za ku iya farawa, da duk wani abu da zai shafi wuri ko balaguro.",
  "A stronger Jobs profile improves recruiter confidence and gives your application more proof.": "Bayanan Jobs masu ƙarfi suna ƙara amincewar mai daukar aiki kuma suna ƙara hujja ga aikace-aikacenka.",
  "About the team": "Game da ƙungiya",
  "Account-level identity, password, session security and the unified HenryCo trust score sit at the account-hub level — every division (Jobs, Care, Studio, Marketplace, Learn, Property, Logistics) reads from the same record.": "Ainihin asusun, kalmar sirri, tsaron zama, da hadaddiyar ƙimar amincewar HenryCo suna a matakin cibiyar asusu — kowane sashe (Jobs, Care, Studio, Marketplace, Learn, Property, Logistics) yana karantawa daga rikodi iri ɗaya.",
