  "As soon as candidates apply, they will appear here and in the employer applicant queue.": "Da zarar 'yan takara suka nemi, za su bayyana a nan da kuma a layin mai daukar ma'aikatan.",
  "As soon as roles start receiving applications, this feed will show the newest candidates entering your hiring pipeline.": "Da zarar matsayin sun fara karɓar aikace-aikace, wannan tafiya zai nuna sabbin 'yan takara da ke shiga bututun aiki.",
  "At least four clear skills and preferred functions improve role matching.": "Aƙalla ƙwarewa huɗu masu bayyana da abubuwan da kuke so suna ƙara dacewar matsayi.",
  "Audit trail for jobs, verification, and application movement.": "Hanyar binciken don ayyuka, tabbatarwa, da motsi na aikace-aikace.",
  "Awaiting candidates": "Ana jiran 'yan takara",
