  "Basics and identity": "Tushe da ainihi",
  "Before we call an employer verified, we look at who they are, how they show up publicly, and whether their story matches the roles they post. Pending does not always mean “bad” — it can simply mean “still in review.”": "Kafin mu kira mai daukar aiki da aka tabbatar, muna duba waye su, yadda suke bayyana a fili, da ko labarinsu ya dace da matsayin da suka wallafa. \"Yana jira\" ba koyaushe yana nufin \"mara kyau\" ba — yana iya kawai nufin \"har yanzu yana cikin bita.\"",
  "Benefits": "Fa'idoji",
  "Benefits & what they want you to know": "Fa'idoji da abin da suke son ka sani",
