  "Browse all roles": "Bincika dukan matsayoyi",
  "Browse open roles and apply to the ones that interest you. Your applications will appear here with stage updates.": "Bincika matsayoyin da ke buɗe kuma ka nemi waɗanda suke jan ra'ayinka. Aikace-aikacenka za su bayyana a nan tare da sabuntawar matakai.",
  "Build a shortlist worth revisiting.": "Gina jeri mai kyau wanda ya cancanci komawa.",
  "Built from profile completeness, verification status, and hiring activity.": "An gina daga cikar bayanan, matsayin tabbatarwa, da ayyukan daukar aiki.",
  "Candidate": "Mai nema",
  "Candidate Detail": "Cikakken bayanin mai nema",
