  "Candidate movement will appear here.": "Motsi na mai nema zai bayyana a nan.",
  "Candidate profiles": "Bayanan masu nema",
  "Candidates": "Masu nema",
  "Candidates across your roles.": "Masu nema a tsakanin matsayoyinka.",
  "Candidates and employers use the same platform with different workspaces. If something here does not match what you see on screen, contact": "Masu nema da masu daukar aiki suna amfani da dandali iri ɗaya da sararin aiki daban-daban. Idan wani abu a nan bai dace da abin da kake gani a allon ba, tuntubi",
  "Careers at HenryCo": "Sana'o'i a HenryCo",
  "Category slug": "Slug na rukuni",
  "Check back later or browse other open positions on the board.": "Sake duba bayan, ko ka bincika sauran wuraren da ke buɗe a allo.",
  "Check back soon or browse external roles from verified employers on the main board.": "Sake duba ba da daɗewa ba, ko ka bincika matsayoyin waje daga masu daukar aiki da aka tabbatar a babban allo.",
  "Check pay, title, start date, and who you report to. It is OK to ask quiet questions before you say yes.": "Bincika albashi, taken, ranar farawa, da wanda kake ba da rahoto a gareshi. Babu laifi a yi tambayoyi a hankali kafin ka ce eh.",
  "Communication": "Sadarwa",
