  "Compensation discussed in process": "Za a tattauna diyya yayin aiki",
  "Complete your profile first": "Da farko cika bayananka",
  "Congratulations. Tidy up saved roles and applications so your hub reflects where you are headed next.": "Taya murna. Tsaftace matsayoyin da aka adana da aikace-aikace don cibiyarka ta nuna inda za ka.",
  "Conversations & alerts": "Tattaunawa da faɗakarwa",
  "Create a free account": "Ƙirƙiri asusun kyauta",
  "Create an alert": "Ƙirƙiri faɗakarwa",
  "Create your first live role alert.": "Ƙirƙiri faɗakarwa ta farko ta matsayi kai tsaye.",
  "Cross-employer applicant movement in one structured table.": "Motsi na masu nema a tsakanin masu daukar aiki a tebur ɗaya da aka tsara.",
  "Culture & values": "Al'adu da ƙimomi",
  "Deeper conversations or tasks so both sides can judge fit with real examples.": "Tattaunawa mai zurfi ko ayyuka don ɓangarorin biyu su iya yanke shawara akan dacewa da misalai na gaske.",
  "Discussed in process": "Ana tattauna yayin aiki",
  "Discussed with the hiring team": "An tattauna da ƙungiyar daukar aiki",
  "Email not supplied": "Ba a samar da imel ba",
  "Email, WhatsApp and in-app notifications — quiet hours and digest cadence are set in your account preferences.": "Imel, WhatsApp da sanarwa na cikin manhaja — lokutan natsuwa da yawan taƙaitawa ana saita su a cikin abubuwan da kuke so na asusun.",
  "Employer": "Mai daukar aiki",
  "Employer Settings": "Saitin mai daukar aiki",
  "Employer pages with verified state.": "Shafukan masu daukar aiki da matsayin tabbatarwa.",
  "Employer profiles in the system.": "Bayanan masu daukar aiki a tsarin.",
  "Employer profiles linked to your account.": "Bayanan masu daukar aiki da aka haɗa da asusunka.",
  "Employer profiles under management.": "Bayanan masu daukar aiki da ake sarrafawa.",
  "Employer profiles with verification maturity visible to candidates.": "Bayanan masu daukar aiki da matakin tabbatar wanda 'yan takara ke iya gani.",
  "Employer trust": "Amana ga mai daukar aiki",
  "Employer verification": "Tabbatar mai daukar aiki",
  "Employer workspace": "Sararin aiki na mai daukar aiki",
  "Employers": "Masu daukar aiki",
  "Every applicant thread surfaces in your candidate inbox and in the unified /messages view across HenryCo.": "Kowane zaren mai nema yana bayyana a akwatin shigarka na 'yan takara da kuma a haɗaɗɗen ra'ayin /messages a HenryCo.",
  "Every application gets a stage you can read in your candidate hub — no more wondering if your CV vanished. The steps below are what this employer asked us to show for this role; your own timeline may skip or repeat steps, but updates stay in one place.": "Kowace aikace-aikace na samun matakin da za ka iya karantawa a cibiyar 'yan takararka — babu sake mamakin idan CV ɗinka ya ɓace. Matakai a ƙasa su ne abin da mai daukar wannan aikin ya nemi mu nuna; layin lokacinka na iya tsallake ko maimaita matakai, amma sabuntawa suna kasancewa a wuri ɗaya.",
  "Explore roles first": "Da farko bincika matsayoyin",
  "Final conversations, decision, and a clear outcome either way.": "Tattaunawa ta ƙarshe, yanke shawara, da sakamako bayyananne ta ko wace hanya.",
  "Finish one profile piece": "Kammala sashen bayani ɗaya",
  "Follow every role you've applied to, with clear stages and updates from hiring teams.": "Bi kowane matsayi da kuka nema, da bayyanannun matakai da sabuntawa daga ƙungiyoyin daukar aiki.",
  "Free credits and featured-listing fees draw from the same balance you use across Marketplace, Studio and Property. Team-seat invoicing is owner-flagged — contact support if your headcount needs a seat plan.": "Cancantar kyauta da kuɗin jeri na musamman suna fitowa daga ma'auni iri ɗaya da kake amfani da shi a Marketplace, Studio, da Property. An yi wa biyan kuɗi na kujerar ƙungiya alamar mai shi — tuntubi tallafi idan adadin ma'aikatanka na buƙatar shirin kujeru.",
  "Full name, phone, and location give recruiters a usable contact layer.": "Cikakken suna, waya, da wuri suna ba masu daukar aiki tushen sadarwa mai amfani.",
  "Get notified when new roles match what you're looking for.": "Karɓi sanarwa idan sabbin matsayoyi sun dace da abin da kake nema.",
  "Headline and summary make the profile readable instead of blank metadata.": "Take da takaitawa suna sa bayanan su zama mai karantawa maimakon metadata maras komai.",
  "HenryCo internal openings running inside the same platform.": "Wuraren shiga na cikin HenryCo da ke aiki a dandali iri ɗaya.",
  "High trust employer": "Mai daukar aiki da amana mai girma",
  "High-level jobs platform telemetry for operators and leadership.": "Telemetri na dandalin Jobs na manyan matakai don masu aiki da shugabanci.",
  "Hiring alerts": "Faɗakarwar daukar aiki",
  "Hiring process": "Tsarin daukar aiki",
  "How HenryCo hires": "Yadda HenryCo ke daukar ma'aikata",
  "How applying works": "Yadda nema ke aiki",
  "Identity & access": "Ainihi da samun dama",
  "Identity, hiring channels and billing — every change syncs to every job posting and every conversation.": "Ainihi, hanyoyin daukar aiki da biyan kuɗi — kowane canji yana daidaita da kowane sanarwar aiki da kowace tattaunawa.",
  "If it still feels right, send a short, specific note while it is open.": "Idan har yanzu yana ji daidai, aika gajeren bayani na musamman yayin da yake buɗe.",
  "Improve profile strength": "Inganta ƙarfin bayani",
  "In a few sentences: why this role, why now, and proof you have done this work before.": "A cikin jumloli kaɗan: dalilin wannan matsayi, dalilin yanzu, da hujjar cewa ka taɓa yin wannan aikin.",
  "Inbound applicant messages, interview reminders and hiring nudges all route through the unified HenryCo notification rail. Manage channels in your account preferences.": "Sakonni masu shigowa daga masu nema, tunatarwa na hira da turaren daukar aiki duk suna wucewa ta hanyar haɗaɗɗiyar layin sanarwa na HenryCo. Sarrafa hanyoyin a abubuwan da kuke so na asusunka.",
  "Internal openings go through the same clear, structured hiring process as every role on the platform. Apply with your HenryCo account and track progress in your candidate hub.": "Wuraren shiga na ciki suna ratsa tsari iri ɗaya na daukar aiki kamar kowane matsayi a dandali. Nemi tare da asusun HenryCo ka kuma bibiyar ci gaba a cibiyarka.",
  "Internal tracks": "Hanyoyin ciki",
  "Interview prep for this role": "Shirye-shiryen tambayoyi don wannan matsayin",
  "Interview season—prep like you mean it": "Lokacin tambayoyi — shirya kamar yadda ya kamata",
  "Interview stages": "Matakan tambayoyi",
  "Interview stages (plain English)": "Matakan tambayoyi (a sauƙin harshe)",
  "Interview-ready": "Shiryayye don tambayoyi",
  "Interviewing": "Ana tambayoyi",
