  "New and edited job posts can be checked for scams, unclear pay, or misleading titles. If we need changes, we explain why. The goal is fewer wasted applications for candidates and fewer unserious posts for employers.": "Sabbin sanarwowin aiki da aka gyara ana iya bincika don zamba, biya marasa fayyace, ko taken ƙarya. Idan mun buƙaci canje-canje, mun bayyana dalili. Manufar: rage aikace-aikacen ɓatattu ga 'yan takara da rage sanarwowin marasa muhimmanci ga masu daukar aiki.",
  "New applications, moderation pressure, and hiring movement will appear here as soon as the live system receives them.": "Sabbin aikace-aikace, matsa lambar sa ido da motsi na daukar aiki za su bayyana a nan da zarar tsarin kai tsaye ya karɓi su.",
  "New employer profiles will appear here when companies register and need verification.": "Sabbin bayanan masu daukar aiki za su bayyana a nan idan kamfanoni suka yi rajista kuma suka nemi tabbatarwa.",
