  "Saving alert...": "Ana adana faɗakarwa…",
  "Saving and applying require a HenryCo account so your shortlist and applications are not floating in a cookie somewhere. You control your profile, documents, and what you send with each application.": "Adana da nema suna buƙatar asusun HenryCo don gajeren jerinka da aikace-aikace ba su yawo a cikin kuki ba. Kai ne ke iko da bayananka, takardun, da abin da kake aikawa tare da kowane aikace-aikace.",
  "Saving is private — employers are not notified. Applying sends this role, your profile, and your note to the hiring team. Either action uses your HenryCo account so nothing gets lost between devices.": "Adana yana keɓance — ba a sanar wa masu daukar aiki ba. Nema yana aika wannan matsayi, bayananka, da bayaninka zuwa ƙungiyar daukar aiki. Ayyukan biyu suna amfani da asusun HenryCo don kada wani abu ya ɓace tsakanin na'urori.",
  "Saving is private. Applying sends your profile.": "Adana yana keɓance. Nema yana aika bayananka.",
