  "Set up your company": "Saita kamfaninka",
  "Shortlist means they liked the match enough to look closer. Have examples ready, know your dates, and watch Applications for the next message.": "Gajeren jeri yana nufin sun fi son daidaitawar har su kalla a kusa. Sami misalai shirye, ka san ranakunka, kuma ka kalli \"Aikace-aikace\" don sako na gaba.",
  "Shortlist moves, interview invites, and offer steps show up in": "Motsi na gajeren jeri, gayyatar tambayoyi, da matakai na tayi suna bayyana a",
  "Shortlisted": "An gajarce",
  "Sign in once at HenryCo and access Jobs as employer, Care as a customer, Studio as a buyer — all from the same identity. Security settings (password, MFA, signed-out sessions) live at the account hub.": "Shiga sau ɗaya a HenryCo kuma ka shiga Jobs a matsayin mai daukar aiki, Care a matsayin abokin ciniki, Studio a matsayin mai siye — duka daga ainihi guda. Saitin tsaro (kalmar sirri, MFA, zaman da aka fita) suna a cibiyar asusu.",
