  "The canonical employer record. Logo, legal name, location, hiring contact and verification documents live here — every job posting reads from this single source.": "Rikodin daidaita na mai daukar aiki. Tambari, sunan doka, wuri, lambar daukar aiki da takardun tabbatarwa suna a nan — kowace sanarwar aiki tana karantawa daga wannan tushen guda.",
  "The latest candidates across your open roles.": "Sabbin 'yan takara a tsakanin matsayoyinka da ke buɗe.",
  "The lists below spell out what you will own and what we need to see in your background. If that sounds like you — and the pay band works for your life — this is worth a thoughtful application.": "Jeruwan da ke ƙasa suna fitar da abin da za ka mallaka da abin da muke buƙatar gani a baya. Idan wannan ya yi kama da kai — kuma adadin albashi ya dace da rayuwarka — wannan ya cancanci aikace-aikace mai zurfi.",
  "The pipeline is quiet right now.": "Bututu yana shiru a yanzu.",
