  "Coordinate the real-world workflow behind trusted property listings: inspections, viewings, inquiry handoff, and managed portfolio continuity.": "Hada hanyar aiki ta gaskiya bayan jeruwan kadarori amintattu: dubawa, kallo, mika tambayoyi, da ci gaba na portfolio da ake gudanarwa.",
