  "Direct uploads are preferred over links for authority, identity, and management review.": "Ɗora kai tsaye ya fi hanyoyin haɗi don bita hukuma, ainihi, da gudanarwa.",
  "Discover": "Gano",
  "District": "Yanki",
  "Docs hold": "An riƙe takardu",
  "Documents": "Takardu",
  "Documents are path-specific, inspections are real workflows, and managed vs non-managed publication is not blurred together. Calm, but serious.": "Takardun suna takamaiman ga kowace hanya, dubawa hanyoyin aiki na gaske ne, kuma wallafa mai gudanarwa da rashin gudanarwa ba a haɗa su ba. Mai natsuwa, amma mai mahimmanci.",
  "Documents read; eligibility and authority assessed.": "An karanta takardu; an tantance cancanta da hukuma.",
  "Each submission is routed by service type, authority reality, inspection sensitivity, and account trust. The form adapts to the path; documents upload directly; the listing stays private until governance clears it.": "Ana tura kowane gabatarwa bisa nau'in sabis, gaskiyar hukuma, hankali na dubawa, da amincewar asusu. Fom yana daidaitawa zuwa hanyar; takardu suna ɗora kai tsaye; jeri yana zama na sirri har sai mulki ya share shi.",
  "Editorial review path": "Hanyar bita ta edita",
  "Editorial review, approval, then publication if quality holds.": "Bita ta edita, amincewa, sannan wallafawa idan inganci ya tsaya.",
  "Eligibility": "Cancanta",
  "Eligibility hold": "An riƙe cancanta",
  "Email and WhatsApp delivery stack for property notifications.": "Tarin bayarwa na imel da WhatsApp don sanarwar kadarori.",
  "Escalated": "An ɗaukaka",
  "Existing media URLs": "URL na media masu wanzuwa",
  "Expected response": "Amsa da ake tsammani",
  "Explain the space, occupancy reality, access conditions, and what makes the listing serious.": "Bayyana wurin, gaskiyar zama, sharuɗɗan shiga, da abin da ke sa jerin ya zama mai mahimmanci.",
  "Filter state stays shareable in the URL, results update without a blunt refresh, and every listing carries trust context before you invest time in it.": "Yanayin matatu yana ci gaba da rabawa a URL, sakamako yana sabuntawa ba tare da sake lodi mai zafi ba, kuma kowace jeri tana ɗaukar yanayin amana kafin ka saka lokacinka.",
  "Find the right place. Keep your filters.": "Sami daidai wuri. Riƙe matatunka.",
  "From": "Daga",
  "Furnished": "Mai kayan ɗaki",
  "Future availability": "Samuwa nan gaba",
  "Generator, smart security, rooftop terrace...": "Janareta, tsaro mai hankali, baranda na sama…",
  "Governance decision": "Yanke shawara na mulki",
  "Governed before it is public.": "Ana mulkar kafin ya zama jama'a.",
  "Headline": "Kanun labari",
  "HenryCo account sign-in": "Shiga asusun HenryCo",
  "HenryCo checks": "Binciken HenryCo",
  "HenryCo expects pricing, media, and listing identity to be strong enough for real decision-making before a property is promoted publicly.": "HenryCo yana tsammanin farashi, mahangar, da ainihin jerin su zama masu ƙarfi don yanke shawara na gaske kafin a tallata kadarar a fili.",
  "HenryCo is involved beyond publication. That usually means clearer viewing coordination, tighter listing upkeep, and a more reliable post-inquiry path.": "HenryCo yana shiga fiye da wallafawa. Yawanci wannan yana nufin haɗakar kallo mai bayyana, kulawar jeri mai tsanani, da hanyar bayan tambaya mai tabbas.",
  "HenryCo keeps this record private first, then decides whether it moves to documents, eligibility, inspection, or editorial review.": "HenryCo yana riƙe wannan rikodin a sirri da farko, sannan ya yanke shawara ko zai shiga zuwa takardu, cancanta, dubawa, ko bita ta edita.",
  "HenryCo may confirm access, location, or listing readiness before the appointment is fixed. If you want to move forward after the viewing, extra documents can still be requested depending on the property and next step.": "HenryCo na iya tabbatar da shiga, wuri, ko shiri na jeri kafin a sanya alƙawari. Idan kana son ci gaba bayan kallo, ana iya buƙatar ƙarin takardu dangane da kadarar da mataki na gaba.",
  "HenryCo uses your account so replies, clarifications, and the next trust checks stay in one place.": "HenryCo yana amfani da asusunka don amsoshi, bayyanawa, da binciken amana na gaba su zauna a wuri ɗaya.",
  "Higher-risk listings can move through extra checks even after they appear live.": "Jeruwan haɗari masu girma na iya wucewa ta ƙarin bita ko da bayan sun bayyana kai tsaye.",
  "Higher-risk property submissions stay in eligibility review until your HenryCo identity verification is approved.": "Gabatarwar kadarar haɗari mai yawa za ta ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin bita ta cancanta har sai an amince da tabbatar da ainihinka na HenryCo.",
  "Highlights": "Manyan abubuwa",
  "Homes and stays already on managed rails.": "Gidaje da zamuna da suka riga sun kasance akan layukan da ake gudanarwa.",
  "Hotspots": "Wuraren zafi",
  "How HenryCo Property governs listing submissions, documents, inspections, managed operations, and publication safety.": "Yadda HenryCo Property ke gudanar da gabatarwar jeri, takardu, dubawa, ayyukan da ake gudanarwa, da amincin wallafawa.",
  "If a viewing is requested, HenryCo may still confirm access, location, or readiness before the appointment.": "Idan an nemi kallo, HenryCo har yanzu na iya tabbatar da shiga, wuri, ko shiri kafin alƙawari.",
  "If assets already exist online, add one URL per line.": "Idan kayan suna riga suna kan layi, ƙara URL ɗaya kowane layi.",
  "If the listing changes materially, it can move back into review.": "Idan jerin ya canza ainihi, zai iya komawa zuwa bita.",
  "If you want to move forward, HenryCo may request identity, affordability, or company documents before the next approval step.": "Idan kana son ci gaba, HenryCo na iya buƙatar takardun ainihi, samar da kuɗi, ko na kamfani kafin mataki na gaba na amincewa.",
  "Inquiries": "Tambayoyi",
  "Inquiries are tied to your HenryCo account so agents can respond securely and you can track follow-up in one place.": "Tambayoyi suna haɗe da asusunka na HenryCo don wakilai su iya amsa lafiya kuma za ka iya bibiyar biyo baya a wuri ɗaya.",
  "Inquiry": "Tambaya",
  "Inquiry and viewing flows will create support context here when they need attention.": "Hanyoyin tambaya da kallo za su ƙirƙiri yanayin tallafi a nan idan suka buƙaci kulawa.",
  "Inquiry status": "Matsayin tambaya",
  "Inquiry submitted. HenryCo Property has placed it in the follow-up queue and the next response will stay tied to your account.": "An gabatar da tambaya. HenryCo Property ta sanya ta a layin biyo baya kuma amsa ta gaba za ta zauna a haɗe da asusunka.",
