  "Support and escalation context": "Yanayin tallafi da ɗaukakawa",
  "Support can see the inquiry queue, viewing queue, and the shared support threads generated from property activity.": "Tallafi zai iya ganin layin tambaya, layin kallo, da zaren tallafi da aka raba waɗanda aka samar daga aikin kadarar.",
  "Support threads": "Zaren tallafi",
  "Tenant communication, inspections, reporting, maintenance coordination, short-let operations, and owner trust workflows — held on one operating rail rather than scattered across apps and chat threads.": "Sadarwar mai haya, dubawa, rahoto, daidaita gyare-gyare, ayyukan hayar gajere, da hanyoyin amana na mai shi — akan layi guda na aiki maimakon a tarwatse a cikin manhajoji da hira.",
  "The essentials renters, buyers, owners, and managed-property clients usually check before a viewing or submission.": "Mahimman abubuwan da masu hayar gida, masu siye, masu shi, da abokan cinikin kadarar da ake gudanarwa galibi suke bincike kafin kallo ko gabatarwa.",
  "The listing form unlocks after you sign in. Use the panel on the left, or": "Fom na jeri yana buɗewa bayan ka shiga. Yi amfani da panel a hagu, ko",
  "This listing is not appearing here as an untouched upload. HenryCo has already reviewed the record before showing it publicly.": "Wannan jerin ba ya bayyana a nan a matsayin loda kawai. HenryCo ya riga ya bita rikodin kafin ya nuna shi a fili.",
  "This path is inspection-led rather than publication-led. HenryCo still needs the location, authority, and access truth before deciding whether the property can move into a public listing workflow.": "Wannan hanyar ana jagorantar ta da dubawa maimakon wallafawa. HenryCo har yanzu yana buƙatar gaskiyar wuri, hukuma, da shiga kafin ya yanke shawarar ko kadarar za ta iya shiga hanyar jerin jama'a.",
  "Tracked in the HenryCo account timeline.": "Ana bibiya a layin lokacin asusun HenryCo.",
  "Trade-offs": "Sasantawa",
  "Trust evidence": "Hujjar amana",
  "Trust notes": "Bayanin amana",
  "Trust notes stay visible so seekers understand what has been checked.": "Bayanin amana yana ci gaba da bayyana don masu nema su fahimci abin da aka bincika.",
  "Trust routing": "Tura amana",
  "Trust standards | HenryCo Property": "Ka'idojin amana | HenryCo Property",
  "Try broadening the area, removing one filter at a time, or switching from a precise phrase to the property type you want HenryCo to surface.": "Gwada faɗaɗa yanki, cire matata ɗaya a lokaci ɗaya, ko canzawa daga jumla mai daidai zuwa nau'in kadarar da kake son HenryCo ya nuna.",
