  "Upload the real evidence directly. HenryCo stores review files against the listing so staff can assess them without chasing pasted links.": "Ɗora ainihin hujja kai tsaye. HenryCo yana adana fayilolin bita tare da jerin don ma'aikata su iya kimanta su ba tare da bin haɗin da aka manna ba.",
  "Uploading media and trust files without leaving the page": "Ɗora mahangar da fayilolin amana ba tare da barin shafin ba",
