  "Be specific. We read every field. Vague pitches or missing proof slow the process down. Honesty about your availability and experience speeds it up.": "Ka kasance takamaiman. Muna karanta kowane filin. Furucin marasa cikakke ko rashin hujja suna jinkirta tafiyar. Gaskiya game da samuwarka da kwarewarka tana hanzartawa.",
