  "Browse practical HenryCo courses you can finish, with clear progress and credentials employers can verify.": "Bincika kwasoshin HenryCo masu amfani da za ka iya kammalawa, da bayyananniyar ci gaba da takaddun shaida masu daukar aiki za su iya tabbatar.",
