  "Certificates issued": "Takaddun shaida da aka fitar",
  "Certificates stay tied to enrollments and public verification codes so the academy can prove what was earned.": "Takaddun shaida suna ci gaba da haɗewa da rajistar da lambobin tabbatarwa na jama'a don makaranta ta iya tabbatar abin da aka samu.",
  "Certification course": "Kwas na takardar shaida",
  "Choose a program, sign in, learn in order, and (where the course includes it) pass a short assessment to unlock your certificate. Assigned training from managers appears in the same place.": "Zaɓi shiri, shiga, koya bisa tsari, kuma (idan kwas yana da shi) ka ci nasara akan ɗan gwaji don buɗe takardar shaidarka. Horon da manajojin suka sanya yana bayyana a wuri ɗaya.",
  "Choose course": "Zaɓi kwas",
  "Choose path": "Zaɓi hanya",
  "Click a course to view enrolments, syllabus, and credentials issued so far.": "Latsa kwas don ganin rajistar, manhajar, da takaddun shaidar da aka fitar har yanzu.",
  "Comma-separated tags": "Alamomi da aka raba da waƙafi",
  "Commission is deducted at sale and disclosed in the instructor agreement before publishing opens. Featured placement (paid promotion in search results) is coming soon — separate from the base commission.": "Ana cire kwamiti a lokacin sayar da kuma bayyana shi a yarjejeniyar malami kafin a buɗe wallafawa. Sanya ƙwararru (talla a sakamakon binciken) yana zuwa nan ba da daɗewa ba — daban da kwamitin tushe.",
  "Completion and assessment status are tied to the course enrollment path.": "Matsayin kammalawa da tantance suna haɗe da hanyar rajistar kwas.",
  "Completion based on real enrollment status and verified academy progress.": "Kammalawa bisa matsayin rajista na gaske da ci gaban makaranta da aka tabbatar.",
  "Completion follows each course’s rules — usually all lessons, then a passing quiz where applicable. Status shows plainly in the learning room.": "Kammalawa tana bin ka'idodin kowane kwas — yawanci dukan darussa, sannan jarrabawa idan ya dace. Matsayi yana bayyana sosai a cikin ɗakin koyo.",
  "Completion logic derived from real enrollments.": "Tunanin kammalawa daga rajistar gaske.",
  "Completion rate": "Adadin kammala",
  "Completion rate compares completed enrolments against total enrolments.": "Adadin kammala yana kwatanta rajistar da aka kammala da jimillar rajista.",
