  "Courses currently represented in the academy data layer.": "Kwasoshin da ake wakilta a yanzu a matakin bayanan makaranta.",
  "Create Account": "Ƙirƙiri asusu",
  "Create a free HenryCo account first—it takes a minute. Then return to any course and tap Start this course (or complete checkout if the program is paid).": "Da farko ƙirƙiri asusun HenryCo na kyauta — yana ɗaukar minti ɗaya. Sannan komawa zuwa kowane kwas kuma latsa Fara wannan kwas (ko kammala biya idan shirin yana da kuɗi).",
  "Create courses and assemble lesson sequences.": "Ƙirƙiri kwasoshi kuma haɗa jerin darussa.",
  "Credentials": "Takaddun shaida",
  "Curating the latest HenryCo Learn programs so every page opens with live content and a calm reading experience.": "Ana zaɓar shirye-shiryen HenryCo Learn na ƙarshe don kowane shafi ya buɗe da abun ciki kai tsaye da gogewar karatu cikin natsuwa.",
  "Decline application": "Ƙi aikace-aikace",
  "Define the course metadata, then add modules + lessons. Lessons can be video (Cloudinary), reading (markdown), quiz (assessment), or assignment (file or free-text submission).": "Bayyana metadata na kwas, sannan ƙara modules + darussa. Darussa za su iya zama bidiyo (Cloudinary), karatu (markdown), tambaya (tantance), ko aiki (fayil ko rubutu kyauta).",
  "Define the syllabus": "Bayyana manhajar",
  "Distinct learner identities with live academy activity.": "Ainihin ɗaliban dabam-daban da ayyukan makaranta kai tsaye.",
  "Download certificate": "Sauke takardar shaida",
  "Download-ready and publicly verifiable": "Shirye don saukewa kuma za a iya tabbatar a fili",
