  "Duration label, e.g. 2h 15m": "Lakabin tsawon lokaci, misali 2h 15m",
  "Each card opens the full course page: what you’ll learn, how long it takes, whether there’s an assessment, and how to enroll.": "Kowane kati yana buɗe cikakken shafin kwas: abin da za ka koya, tsawon lokaci, ko akwai tantance, da yadda za a yi rajista.",
  "Each completed enrollment under your courses contributes to the gross figure. Net payout reflects HenryCo's platform fee per your payout model.": "Kowane rajistar da aka kammala a karkashin kwasoshinka yana ba da gudummawa ga jimillar. Biyan kuɗi mai tsabta yana nuna kuɗin dandali na HenryCo bisa ga tsarinka na biya.",
  "Each lesson unlocks the next. Finish in order — no skipping.": "Kowace darasi yana buɗe na gaba. Ka kammala bisa tsari — ba tare da tsallakewa ba.",
  "Earned certificate": "Takardar shaida da aka samu",
  "Eligible courses issue a certificate with a code anyone can verify online — useful for employers, partners, or your own records.": "Kwasoshin da suka cancanta suna fitar da takardar shaida da lambar da kowa zai iya tabbatar a layi — mai amfani ga masu daukar aiki, abokan haɗin gwiwa, ko bayananka.",
  "Eligible learners receive a downloadable certificate and a verification code employers or partners can check online.": "Ɗaliban da suka cancanta suna karɓar takardar shaidar da za a iya saukewa da lambar tabbatarwa wadda masu daukar aiki ko abokan haɗin gwiwa za su iya bincika a layi.",
  "Enroll & learn": "Yi rajista & koya",
  "Enroll to unlock the full sequence.": "Yi rajista don buɗe cikakken jeri.",
  "Enrolled": "An yi rajista",
  "Enrolling you now...": "Ana yin rajistar ka yanzu…",
  "Enrollment is marked completed in the academy record.": "An yi alama da rajistar an kammala a rikodin makaranta.",
  "Enter or follow a verification code to see the official record: learner name, course, issue date, and status. This is the same check employers and partners use—no login required.": "Shigar ko bi lambar tabbatarwa don ganin rikodin hukuma: sunan ɗalibi, kwas, ranar bayarwa, da matsayi. Wannan shi ne bincike iri ɗaya da masu daukar aiki da abokan haɗin gwiwa ke amfani da shi — ba a buƙatar shiga.",
  "Estimated minutes": "Mintunan da ake hasashe",
  "Estimated read": "Karatun da ake hasashe",
  "Every application receives a written decision: approved, change-request, or decline. No silent rejections.": "Kowane aikace-aikace yana karɓar shawarar da aka rubuta: an amince, an nemi canji, ko an ƙi. Babu ƙin yarda a shiru.",
  "Every field here is a server action — saving updates the live catalogue. Keep titles plain, descriptions outcome-focused, and the syllabus tight.": "Kowane filin a nan aikin sabar ne — adanawa yana sabunta kasidar kai tsaye. Riƙe take a sauƙi, bayanai masu mai da hankali ga sakamako, da manhajar a takaice.",
  "Every lesson marked complete": "Kowace darasi an yi alama da kammalawa",
  "Every lesson stays attached to its real course and module so progress, certificates, learner dashboards, and public pages remain in sync.": "Kowace darasi tana ci gaba da haɗewa da kwas ɗinta na gaske da module don ci gaba, takaddun shaida, dashboard na ɗalibai, da shafukan jama'a su kasance daidai.",
  "Existing courses": "Kwasoshin da suke",
  "Expertise": "Ƙwarewa",
  "Explain what was approved, what needs to change, or why the team passed.": "Bayyana abin da aka amince, abin da yake buƙatar canji, ko dalilin da yasa ƙungiyar ta ƙi.",
