  "Learner identifiers are not displayed in this surface — only aggregate counts. Reviews shown here are those published by learners and approved by content moderation.": "Ba a nuna ainihin ɗalibai a wannan fuska ba — ƙididdiga gabaɗaya ne kawai. Bita da ake nuna a nan su ne waɗanda ɗalibai suka wallafa kuma sa ido na abun ciki ya amince da su.",
  "Learner operations stay tied to live academy records so course status, assignments, and certificate eligibility stay consistent.": "Ayyukan ɗalibi suna ci gaba da haɗewa da bayanan makaranta na kai tsaye don matsayin kwas, ayyuka, da cancantar takardar shaida su kasance daidai.",
