  "Learning paths let HenryCo Learn present capability ladders instead of loose course lists.": "Hanyoyin koyo suna ba HenryCo Learn damar gabatar da matakan ƙwarewa maimakon jerin kwasoshi marasa tsari.",
  "Learning room": "Ɗakin koyo",
