  "Lesson title": "Taken darasi",
  "Lessons are complete. Submit the assessment to unlock final completion and certification.": "Darussa sun cika. Gabatar da tantance don buɗe kammala ƙarshe da takardar shaida.",
  "Lessons are meant to be taken in order. When you're enrolled, each step unlocks as you finish the one before it. If this program includes a certificate, you'll see exactly what you must complete—including any final quiz and passing score—inside your learning room and in your HenryCo account.": "Darussa an tsara su don a koya bisa tsari. Lokacin da kake rajista, kowane mataki yana buɗewa yayin da kake kammala wanda ke kafinsa. Idan wannan shiri ya haɗa da takardar shaida, za ka ga ainihin abin da dole ne ka kammala — gami da kowane tantance na ƙarshe da maki na nasara — a cikin ɗakin koyo da asusunka na HenryCo.",
  "Lessons in order—so you always know what's next.": "Darussa bisa tsari — don ka san abin da ke gaba kullum.",
  "Lessons inside a module are open in any order. The next module opens once you finish the current one.": "Darussa cikin module suna a buɗe a kowane tsari. Module na gaba yana buɗewa lokacin da ka kammala na yanzu.",
