  "Onboarding": "Haɗawa",
  "Once a learner uploads a file or free-text response, the entry lands here. Instructor grading writes to learn_assignment_grades.": "Da zarar ɗalibi ya ɗora fayil ko amsa mai rubutu kyauta, shigarwar tana sauka a nan. Ƙididdiga ta malami tana rubutu zuwa learn_assignment_grades.",
  "Only some courses award one. Finish every required lesson and meet any quiz rules; your learning room shows a checklist. Then download from the room or view under": "Wasu kwasoshi ne kawai suke bayarwa. Kammala kowace darasi mai mahimmanci kuma cika ka'idodin tambaya; ɗakin koyonka yana nuna jerin abubuwan dubawa. Sai ka sauke daga ɗaki ko kallo a ƙarƙashin",
