  "Outlines, outcomes, and respect for learners’ time matter as much as charisma. We decline proposals that look generic, thin, or misaligned with HenryCo audiences.": "Tsare-tsare, sakamako, da girmama lokacin ɗalibai suna da muhimmanci kamar yadda kwarjini yake. Muna ƙin shawarwarin da suka yi kama da na yau da kullum, marasa zurfi, ko marasa daidaitawa da masu sauraron HenryCo.",
