  "Paths group related courses so you build a capability step by step—ideal when you’re onboarding to a role or deepening a specialty.": "Hanyoyi suna haɗa kwasoshi masu alaƙa don ka gina ƙwarewa mataki-mataki — daidai lokacin shiga matsayi ko zurfafa ƙwarewa.",
  "Payout history": "Tarihin biya",
  "Payout model": "Tsarin biya",
  "Payouts": "Biya",
  "Payouts are released after the 7-day refund window closes for each enrollment that contributes to the period. Status moves from pending → approved → paid.": "Ana sakin biya bayan tagar maido kuɗi ta kwana 7 ta rufe ga kowace rajistar da ke ba da gudummawa ga lokacin. Matsayi yana motsi daga jira → amincewa → biya.",
  "Pending payouts": "Biya da ke jira",
  "Per course": "Kowane kwas",
  "Pick a course, move through lessons in order, track progress in your HenryCo account, and earn a certificate others can verify online. Built for busy adults who want clarity, not jargon.": "Zaɓi kwas, motsa cikin darussa bisa tsari, bibiyar ci gabanka a asusunka na HenryCo, kuma sami takardar shaida da wasu za su iya tabbatar a layi. An gina shi don manya masu aiki da suke son tsabta, ba kalmomi masu rikitarwa ba.",
  "Pick a course, then add a module or extend an existing one with a new lesson. Lesson body uses markdown; video lessons reference a Cloudinary URL.": "Zaɓi kwas, sannan ƙara module ko fadada wani da ke akwai da sabuwar darasi. Jikin darasi yana amfani da markdown; darussan bidiyo suna nuni zuwa URL na Cloudinary.",
