  "Send a message": "Aika sako",
  "Send a note about certificates, enrollment, assignments, or billing. Include your course name and account email so the academy team can help without back-and-forth.": "Aika bayani game da takaddun shaida, rajista, ayyuka, ko biya. Haɗa sunan kwas da imel na asusu domin ƙungiyar makaranta ta iya taimaka ba tare da komawa baya da gaba ba.",
