  "Where a program is paid, HenryCo may offer revenue share or other instructor compensation. Terms are agreed in writing after approval—they are not promised on this page and vary by program. We never ask for payment to review your application.": "如果项目是付费的，HenryCo 可能会提供收入分成或其他讲师报酬。条款在批准后以书面形式达成一致——本页并未承诺这些条款，并且因计划而异。我们从不要求付款来审核您的申请。",
