  "Every application gets a stage you can read in your candidate hub — no more wondering if your CV vanished. The steps below are what this employer asked us to show for this role; your own timeline may skip or repeat steps, but updates stay in one place.": "每份申请都会在您的候选人中心显示阶段——再也无需猜测您的简历是否石沉大海。下方步骤是此雇主针对该岗位要求展示的;您的实际流程可能跳过或重复某些步骤,但更新始终集中在一处。",
  "Explore roles first": "先浏览岗位",
