  "Free credits and featured-listing fees draw from the same balance you use across Marketplace, Studio and Property. Team-seat invoicing is owner-flagged — contact support if your headcount needs a seat plan.": "免费额度与精选展示费均扣减自您在 Marketplace、Studio、Property 共用的余额。团队席位计费由业主标记——如团队规模需要席位方案,请联系客服。",
  "Full name, phone, and location give recruiters a usable contact layer.": "全名、电话与所在地为招聘官提供可用的联系层。",
