  "Inbound applicant messages, interview reminders and hiring nudges all route through the unified HenryCo notification rail. Manage channels in your account preferences.": "申请人来信、面试提醒与招聘推送均通过 HenryCo 的统一通知通道流转。请在账户偏好中管理通道。",
