  "Documents": "文档",
  "Documents are path-specific, inspections are real workflows, and managed vs non-managed publication is not blurred together. Calm, but serious.": "文档因路径而异,验房是实际工作流,托管与非托管发布不会混淆。冷静而严肃。",
  "Documents read; eligibility and authority assessed.": "文档已审阅;资格与权属已评估。",
  "Each submission is routed by service type, authority reality, inspection sensitivity, and account trust. The form adapts to the path; documents upload directly; the listing stays private until governance clears it.": "每次提交按服务类型、权属实情、验房敏感度与账户信任度进行分流。表单按路径自适应;文档直接上传;在治理放行前,房源保持私有。",
  "Editorial review path": "编辑审查路径",
