  "Explain the space, occupancy reality, access conditions, and what makes the listing serious.": "请说明空间、入住实情、出入条件,以及使此房源严肃可信的要素。",
  "Filter state stays shareable in the URL, results update without a blunt refresh, and every listing carries trust context before you invest time in it.": "筛选状态可通过 URL 共享,结果无需粗暴刷新即可更新,每条房源在你投入时间前都带有信任上下文。",
