  "Governed before it is public.": "公开前先治理。",
  "Headline": "标题",
  "HenryCo account sign-in": "登录 HenryCo 账户",
  "HenryCo checks": "HenryCo 核查",
  "HenryCo expects pricing, media, and listing identity to be strong enough for real decision-making before a property is promoted publicly.": "HenryCo 期望在公开推广房源前,定价、素材和挂牌身份足够扎实,可支持真实决策。",
  "HenryCo is involved beyond publication. That usually means clearer viewing coordination, tighter listing upkeep, and a more reliable post-inquiry path.": "HenryCo 在发布之后仍持续参与。这通常意味着更清晰的看房协调、更严密的房源维护,以及更可靠的咨询后路径。",
  "HenryCo keeps this record private first, then decides whether it moves to documents, eligibility, inspection, or editorial review.": "HenryCo 先将此记录置于私有,再决定是否进入文档、资格、验房或编辑审查阶段。",
  "HenryCo may confirm access, location, or listing readiness before the appointment is fixed. If you want to move forward after the viewing, extra documents can still be requested depending on the property and next step.": "HenryCo 可能在确定预约前核实出入、位置或房源准备情况。若您看房后希望继续推进,后续仍可能根据房源与下一步流程要求补充文件。",
  "HenryCo uses your account so replies, clarifications, and the next trust checks stay in one place.": "HenryCo 使用您的账户,使回复、澄清与后续信任核查集中在一处。",
  "Higher-risk listings can move through extra checks even after they appear live.": "高风险房源即使上线后仍可能经历额外核查。",
  "Higher-risk property submissions stay in eligibility review until your HenryCo identity verification is approved.": "高风险房源提交将保持在资格审查中,直到您的 HenryCo 身份验证通过。",
  "Highlights": "亮点",
  "Homes and stays already on managed rails.": "已纳入托管链路的住宅与短住房源。",
  "Hotspots": "热点",
  "How HenryCo Property governs listing submissions, documents, inspections, managed operations, and publication safety.": "HenryCo Property 如何治理房源提交、文档、验房、托管运营与发布安全。",
  "If a viewing is requested, HenryCo may still confirm access, location, or readiness before the appointment.": "如要求看房,HenryCo 仍可能在预约前核实出入、位置或准备情况。",
  "If assets already exist online, add one URL per line.": "若资源已存在于网上,请每行添加一个 URL。",
  "If the listing changes materially, it can move back into review.": "若房源出现实质性变更,可重新进入审查。",
  "If you want to move forward, HenryCo may request identity, affordability, or company documents before the next approval step.": "若您希望继续推进,HenryCo 可能在下一审批步骤前要求身份、付款能力或公司文档。",
  "Inquiries": "咨询",
  "Inquiries are tied to your HenryCo account so agents can respond securely and you can track follow-up in one place.": "咨询与您的 HenryCo 账户绑定,经办人可安全回复,您也可在一处追踪后续。",
