  "Choose a program, sign in, learn in order, and (where the course includes it) pass a short assessment to unlock your certificate. Assigned training from managers appears in the same place.": "选择项目、登录、按顺序学习,并(若课程包含)通过简短测验解锁证书。来自经理的培训分派也显示在同一处。",
