  "Commission is deducted at sale and disclosed in the instructor agreement before publishing opens. Featured placement (paid promotion in search results) is coming soon — separate from the base commission.": "佣金在销售时扣除,并在开放发布前的讲师协议中披露。精选展示(付费推广)即将推出,与基础佣金分开。",
