  "Create a free HenryCo account first—it takes a minute. Then return to any course and tap Start this course (or complete checkout if the program is paid).": "请先创建免费的 HenryCo 账户——只需一分钟。然后回到任意课程并点击「开始此课程」(若为付费,请完成结账)。",
