  "Each completed enrollment under your courses contributes to the gross figure. Net payout reflects HenryCo's platform fee per your payout model.": "您课程下每笔已完成注册都计入毛额。净放款反映 HenryCo 的平台抽成,按您的放款模型计算。",
  "Each lesson unlocks the next. Finish in order — no skipping.": "每节课解锁下一节。请按顺序完成,不要跳过。",
  "Earned certificate": "已获得证书",
  "Eligible courses issue a certificate with a code anyone can verify online — useful for employers, partners, or your own records.": "符合条件的课程颁发带验证码的证书,任何人均可在线核验——便于雇主、合作伙伴或自己的记录。",
  "Eligible learners receive a downloadable certificate and a verification code employers or partners can check online.": "符合条件的学员将获得可下载证书和验证码,雇主或合作方可在线核验。",
  "Enroll & learn": "注册并学习",
