  "Enter or follow a verification code to see the official record: learner name, course, issue date, and status. This is the same check employers and partners use—no login required.": "输入或跟随验证码查看官方记录:学员姓名、课程、签发日期与状态。与雇主和合作方使用的核验相同——无需登录。",
  "Estimated minutes": "预计分钟数",
  "Estimated read": "预计阅读",
