  "Every field here is a server action — saving updates the live catalogue. Keep titles plain, descriptions outcome-focused, and the syllabus tight.": "此处每个字段都是服务器动作——保存即更新实时目录。请保持标题简洁、描述聚焦成果、教学大纲精炼。",
