  "Sign In": "登录",
  "Sign in once. Enrollments, progress, certificates, billing, and teaching applications all live on the same HenryCo profile — no duplicate logins, no parallel inboxes.": "登录一次即可。注册、进度、证书、计费和教学申请皆在同一个 HenryCo 资料下——无重复登录、无并行收件箱。",
  "Sign in to enroll": "登录以注册",
  "Sign in with your HenryCo account, then enroll to begin.": "使用 HenryCo 账户登录,然后注册开始。",
  "Skills that stick. Proof that travels.": "扎实的技能,可携带的证书。",
  "Some courses are assigned inside HenryCo. Team programs appear in your account alongside anything you chose yourself.": "部分课程由 HenryCo 内部分派。团队项目与您自行选择的内容一同显示在账户中。",
