  "You’ll hear from us—or see notes on this page—if we need anything else. While a decision is pending, the form stays closed so reviewers always work from one consistent version.": "如有需要,我们会联系您或在本页留下备注。决定待定期间,表单保持关闭,以便审查者始终基于同一一致版本工作。",
